  "scenes": [
    {
      "text": "Most of what you know about exercise for optimal health is outdated—",
      "imagePath": "images/image_1.png",
      "voicePath": "voice/voice_1.mp3",
      "durationInSeconds": 4.388571428571429,
      "imageWidth": 1024.0,
      "imageHeight": 1024.0
    },
    {
      "text": "one minute of vigorous exercise is worth more than you think.",
      "imagePath": "images/image_2.png",
      "voicePath": "voice/voice_2.mp3",
      "durationInSeconds": 3.526530612244898,
      "imageWidth": 1024.0,
      "imageHeight": 1024.0
    },
    {
      "text": "Current exercise guidelines rely on calories—",
      "imagePath": "images/image_3.png",
      "voicePath": "voice/voice_3.mp3",
      "durationInSeconds": 3.317551020408163,
      "imageWidth": 1024.0,
      "imageHeight": 1024.0
    },
    {
      "text": "suggesting 150 to 300 minutes of moderate activity weekly or half for vigorous.",
      "imagePath": "images/image_4.png",
      "voicePath": "voice/voice_4.mp3",
      "durationInSeconds": 6.295510204081633,
      "imageWidth": 1024.0,
      "imageHeight": 1024.0
    },
    {
      "text": "But a new study flips the script:",
      "imagePath": "images/image_5.png",
      "voicePath": "voice/voice_5.mp3",
      "durationInSeconds": 2.4816326530612245,
      "imageWidth": 1024.0,
      "imageHeight": 1024.0
    },
    {
      "text": "one minute of vigorous exercise delivers outsized benefits.",
      "imagePath": "images/image_6.png",
      "voicePath": "voice/voice_6.mp3",
      "durationInSeconds": 3.7877551020408164,
      "imageWidth": 1024.0,
      "imageHeight": 1024.0
    },
    {
      "text": "Think about a sprint: it can yield more health benefits",
      "imagePath": "images/image_7.png",
      "voicePath": "voice/voice_7.mp3",
      "durationInSeconds": 3.813877551020408,
      "imageWidth": 1024.0,
      "imageHeight": 1024.0
    },
    {
      "text": "than four minutes of a brisk walk.",
      "imagePath": "images/image_8.png",
      "voicePath": "voice/voice_8.mp3",
      "durationInSeconds": 2.246530612244898,
      "imageWidth": 1024.0,
      "imageHeight": 1024.0
    },
    {
      "text": "To really boost your health, picture integrating short, intense bursts,",
      "imagePath": "images/image_9.png",
      "voicePath": "voice/voice_9.mp3",
      "durationInSeconds": 5.433469387755102,
      "imageWidth": 1024.0,
      "imageHeight": 1024.0
    },
    {
      "text": "like a quick jog or some jumping jacks into your routine.",
      "imagePath": "images/image_10.png",
      "voicePath": "voice/voice_10.mp3",
      "durationInSeconds": 3.7355102040816326,
      "imageWidth": 1024.0,
      "imageHeight": 1024.0
    },
    {
      "text": "These vigorous moments pack a punch in reducing disease risks.",
      "imagePath": "images/image_11.png",
      "voicePath": "voice/voice_11.mp3",
      "durationInSeconds": 4.519183673469388,
      "imageWidth": 1024.0,
      "imageHeight": 1024.0
    },
    {
      "text": "To maximize your health gains, try weaving short bursts of intense activity right into your day.",
      "imagePath": "images/image_12.png",
      "voicePath": "voice/voice_12.mp3",
      "durationInSeconds": 6.452244897959184,
      "imageWidth": 1024.0,
      "imageHeight": 1024.0
    },
    {
      "text": "They're more powerful than you might expect.",
      "imagePath": "images/image_13.png",
      "voicePath": "voice/voice_13.mp3",
      "durationInSeconds": 2.3248979591836734,
      "imageWidth": 1024.0,
      "imageHeight": 1024.0
    }
  ],
